data.description: Step into this adorable and well maintained brick ranch boasting 3 bedrooms and 1 bath. Hardwood floors grace the main living areas, adding warmth and charm to the home. An oversized hall closet provides extra storage convenience. Cozy up by the fireplace in the inviting living room, perfect for chilly evenings. Outside, discover a fenced yard with a shed and a workshop with electric included, offering ample space for storage or hobbies. Located in a quiet neighborhood, this home provides a serene and peaceful retreat. Don't miss the chance to make this charming property your new home sweet home!
